article.description: — Quincy Olivari's 22 points helped Xavier defeat Bryant 100-75 on Friday.
article.headline: Xavier defeats Bryant 100-75
article.story: CINCINNATI -- — Quincy Olivari's 22 points helped Xavier defeat Bryant 100-75 on Friday. Olivari added five rebounds and three steals for the Musketeers (4-2). Gytis Nemeiksa scored 14 points and added six rebounds. Dayvion McKnight was 5 of 8 shooting (1 for 3 from 3-point range) to finish with 11 points. Sherif Kenney led the way for the Bulldogs (3-4) with 19 points. Rafael Pinzon added 18 points for Bryant. Doug Edert also recorded 13 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
